            <div class="title">
                House Of Commons Members Fund Bill
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1939-07-13/debates/332a7497-07fb-433b-84e2-8da3ed8a1f0a/WaysAndMeans" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
