                Mr. Magnay
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-07cea35b-70d1-40a5-bf24-e32045555089" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1939-07-13/debates/5fd6a265-fa63-4113-8199-ce9ec812bd39/HouseOfCommonsMembersFundBill#contribution-07cea35b-70d1-40a5-bf24-e32045555089">
