<p class="">Two blacks do not make a white.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-c9030458-ccc9-4ffa-ae71-c5d7975feaa5" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
