            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div>

<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-2837b645-b07c-4af5-ae16-f0416787f924'>
            
<p class="">Bill read a Second time.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div>

<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-10b65d2f-115b-4d65-8468-5ae88a7a1caf'>
            
<p class="">Motion made, and Question put, "That the Bill be committed to a Committee of the Whole House."—[ <em>Captain Margesson</em>]</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div>

<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-43f7dddf-7a20-47d8-b286-de9190d58ce8'>
            
<p class=""><em>The House proceeded to a Division</em>.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div>

<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-3431a578-67e8-4f71-b0f1-0c3a8a08653f'>
            
<p class="">SIR ASSHETON POWNALL and Sir FRANCIS FREMANTLE <em>were appointed Tellers for the Ayes, but there being no Members willing to act as Tellers for the Noes</em>, Mr. SPEAKER <em>declared that the Ayes had it</em>.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div>

<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-ca88eb84-3562-4529-8897-01ca5c928dea'>
            
<p class="">Bill committed to a Committee of the Whole House for Monday next.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
